  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Rocket Bots</i> is a fast-paced, first-person shooter where players defend against relentless waves of hacked robotic enemies in simple compact arenas.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive increasingly brutal waves of rogue bots, from clunky botties to advanced killing machines, using an arsenal of high-tech weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359160/extras/b8892889c59cd1424384b92d072cc180.poster.avif?t=1755423991\" aria-label=\"Gameplay\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359160/extras/b8892889c59cd1424384b92d072cc180.webm?t=1755423991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1359160/extras/b8892889c59cd1424384b92d072cc180.mp4?t=1755423991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Through Steam Workshop, players can design and share custom arenas, shaping their own battlefields for endless replayability. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you claim divine power or fall to the chaos?</p>",
